[52.15649, "o", "# Product Vision: hello-helix\r\n\r\n## Mission\r\n\r\nProvide a simple, reliable temperature conversion tool for the command line.\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nDevelopers frequently need to convert temperatures between Celsius and\r\nFahrenheit while working in terminals and scripts. Searching the web or\r\nwriting throwaway code for this interrupts flow.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\n`hello-helix` is a Node.js CLI that converts temperatures instantly with a\r\n"]
