[54.158965, "o", "# Product Requirements Document: hello-helix\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\n\r\nA Node.js CLI tool that converts temperatures between Celsius and Fahrenheit.\r\n\r\n## Interface\r\n\r\n```\r\nconvert --to-celsius <temp>\r\nconvert --to-fahrenheit <temp>\r\n```\r\n\r\n"]
[54.158998, "o", "Output is a single number rounded to one decimal place, printed to stdout.\r\n\r\n## Priority Matrix\r\n\r\n### P0 -- Basic Conversion (MVP)\r\n\r\n- `convert --to-celsius <temp>` converts Fahrenheit to Celsius.\r\n"]
[54.159182, "o", "...\r\n\r\n"]
