[112.260488, "o", "# TD-001: Temperature Conversion — Technical Design\r\n\r\n## References\r\n\r\n- [FEAT-001](../../01-frame/features/FEAT-001-temperature-conversion.md)\r\n- [PRD](../../01-frame/prd.md)\r\n\r\n## Architecture\r\n\r\nSingle-file implementation: `bin/convert.js`.\r\n\r\nNo external dependencies. The file is both the importable module and the CLI\r\nentry point.\r\n\r\n## Exports\r\n\r\n```js\r\nfunction toFahrenheit(c) // returns (c * 9/5) + 32"]
[112.260516, "o", "\r\nfunction toCelsius(f)    // returns (f - 32) * 5/9\r\n```\r\n"]
